room_title: Escape room "The Night Before Christmas" by Under Lock and Key in Clovis
room_address: 2909 N Prince Street Suite E Clovis, NM 88101
room_description:
Pixie is by far Santa’s orneriest Elf.  He is always pulling pranks!  This time he took things too far!!  He has hidden the magic sleigh bells!  Santa’s can’t leave to deliver gifts without them.

If Christmas is going to happen this year, you’ll need to find those sleigh bells.  Santa is supposed to leave in an hour.  Pixie is a clever trickster; can you find the sleigh bells in time??  Can you save Christmas?
